Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
You know... what do you think of little kids...？
Let's see, they are cheeky sometimes, but basically I like them. They are cute.
Cheeky...？ I see.
When I play with my relatives' children, they sometimes say grown-up things even though they are kids.
...What？
Huh？ ...Am I wrong？
...I see. You're the little kid when you're there.
What are you saying？ Did you misunderstand me？
...Well, it's fine.
Don't convince you're right by yourself. It makes me feel bad.
Rinko
Do you still care about the height difference when you are in a relationship？
That was sudden.
This is about someone I know.
Yes.
When walking side by side on a date, they are very concerned about their short stature.
Is that something you're worried about, ▲小早川＊▲？
This is not about Rinko, I'm talking about someone I know.
I don't know, it's not something that bothers me.
Hey, look at your walking stride.
I always intend to match you pace but, was I going too fast instead, ▲小早川＊▲...？
Suitably... I don't even realized it.
So, I don't think you need to worry about that.
I see... I'll tell it to that someone I know.
Someone, huh.
Yes... someone.
Do you still care about the height thing？
Rinko
I said it was about someone I know.
Ah, I see.
...Yes.
But you know, once you fall in love with someone, such details usually don't matter.
I guess that's how it is.
It's just because most guys don't decide whether or not to date based on height.
I see. That's a bit of a relief.
I knew you cared.
...Well... a little... you know... when we kiss... or something.
...Oh, that's what you meant. But I like the way you try so hard to stand tall when kissing.
...Pervert.
Why would I be that...
"You seem to be concerned all the time, but if you're small in stature, you're small..."
As they say.
Rinko
Don't say small over and over.
...Sometimes it's good to be small, isn't it？
For example...？
Well, it's easier to "princess carry" you... Ah, don't get mad at me.
I'm not angry.
Then why do you look like that？
I wonder what it's like to be a princess... Ah, forget it.
Are you interested？
That's because Rinko is a girl, too... but I don't think I'd want to do it.
Why？ If you want me to, I can always do it, you know？
That's... embarrassing.
If it's where no one is looking, why not？
Yes, that's why... but why Rinko is even... Geez, you're an idiot.
(Why don't you tell me honestly you want to do it.)
Rinko
You know. When you get married, do you want to go on a honeymoon？
...W-what with you all of a sudden？
Don't get me wrong. It's about my dad and... my mother.
Have they at least traveled since they remarried？
No overnight trip, not even a honeymoon.
Busy at work or something？
That's part of it, but they can't leave your kids behind, you know？
Ah. Your brother is still little, right？
Yes. If it's just Rinko, I don't mind if you leave me behind.
It's not a good idea for a girl to live alone, even for a short period of time.
Being alone... I'm used to it. And... I have you now.
...Huh？
Don't imagine anything strange. No one said anything about inviting you over.
If they leave your little brother under your care, can they go on their honeymoon...？
Rinko
It's not so easy. Dad may not be, but... mom is a bit of a worrier.
Hmm...
What？ Did I say something strange！？
I thought you could now say "mom" in a normal way.
...You're an idiot. Mom is just mom...
Yes. Even Rinko won't be a child forever.
I'm glad you've become a "family".
If you keep talking like a guardian like that, you're going to get old fast, you know？
Rinko
So, I gathered up some brochures a while ago, thinking that a nearby hot spring might be a good place for my family to go.
I see. There are so many different plans now.
Yes. If you're close by, it's easy to make a schedule since it's only a night or two away.
Is this the couples-only mixed bathing tour...？
Don't you always find the weirdest things. You dirty devil.
I just happen to find this one！！
I dunno...
That's not the point. Did you talk to your parents about this？
Not yet. It's hard to find the right time to tell them...
But you should just talk to them as soon as possible. You can't decide alone.
Yeah, I know. I'll tell them when I get home today.
Rinko
...Just a few minutes ago, I got a call from home.
From home...？ Is there something wrong...？
Yeah... I was crying.
What？
Rinko was checking travel magazines and such, so they kinda sensed that I was hiding something from them.
At first they were worried that I was going to run away from home again... So I told them the truth.
So that's why you cried on the phone...
Yes. But I cried because I was happy...
You don't have to cry. You're their daughter, you just want them to be happy. That's what I think...
I see. Then, shouldn't you go home early？
...Yeah. Today we're going to plan a trip for the whole family... my mom said.
Well, good for you.
Yes. I'll make sure to report the results later.
You don't have to worry about that. I hope you have a nice trip.
...Yes, thank you.
Rinko
I've been thinking about it lately, I wonder what I will be doing 10 years from now.
I used to think about it a lot... but I keep thinking about the future.
Maybe it's because of me？
Don't be so vain... but you might have some effect, though.
I wonder if you will be working as an office worker or something similar, ▲小早川＊▲.
What do you mean？
Like... not being bound by frameworks... or so I think.
I have no idea. But you will definitely be an old man in 10 years.
...I don't think so.
I mean in the spiritual area. If all you do is take care of others, you'll get old fast, you know？
...Who is getting mold fast？
What did you say？
Nothing.
In the end, what do you think you will be doing in 10 years from now, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Hmm... that's a tough question.
Think about what you want to be in the future.
Well then, a fighter.
...For real？
No way. Did you almost take me seriously？
I've seen you playing a lot of video games.
Hah... An example of people who can't distinguish between reality and fiction...
You don't have to say it that much. So, what do you want to be in the end？
...A secret.
Rinko
What do you think is going to happen to you 10 years from now, rather that Rinko's？
Me, huh... Is it safe to be a salaryman？
I don't mind. Don't you have any more dreams？ That makes you look like an old man.
A dream... If I had a warm home, I would be happy with that alone.
...Yeah, I kinda get that.
Really？
Is that weird？ I used to think there was no such thing as marriage...
Was it triggered by your father's remarriage？
I guess that's part of it. But you know... it's not just that... nevermind.
Don't stop talking.
Shut up... intensive.
10 years from now. It's only fair you tell me. Come on, don't be a wuss.
Rinko
...A bride.
What！？
Hehe, I surprised you！
What a joke.
I'm not even kidding. I'm sure I'll get married one of these days.
I suppose so...
Perhaps you are jealous of my future husband？
...Who know.
Hehe, do your best！
What do you mean？
Who knows！
Are you interested in anything these days, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
I suppose I watch cat videos on popular video sites every day.
I see. Every day, huh？
Yeah. I don't get tired of looking at them every day.
They all have their own personalities, some are cooky, come are timid, and their reactions are all different, you know？
When I see them, I feel like hugging them～～～.
Oh, yeah, you like cats, ▲小早川＊▲.
But you know, I have a problem... Thanks to that, I don't sleep well every day.
You'd better moderate it then.
Yeah. I know, but I find myself staring at it endlessly. It's a sin to be cute...
By the way, do you just watch video sites on the Internet？
Rinko
...Yeah. I don't look around much else. It's my dad's computer to begin with.
Ah, so you don't play games or anything on the internet.
Gaming is still more fun when you're directly beating up your opponent in the arcade.
I don't think I can allow myself to beat you... See, you're a girl, after all.
When playing a fighting game, Rinko is not a girl, she's a fighter.
When we play against each other, it's all girls character.
It's not beautiful if you win using a rugged character. It's my policy.
Rinko
Speaking of the internet, the Killer Bambies' unreleased soundtrack are now available for download.
Ah, the one that's always in your music player, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yes. This song is a live recording, but it's not processed in any weird way, so it has a rough feel to it, which makes it more realistic.
Speaking of which, do you ever go to love shows, ▲小早川＊▲？
Killer Bambies won't be coming to Japan. And I can't go abroad.
I see. Oh, but if you were in a crowded live house, ▲小早川＊▲...
If it's a crowded live house, what...？ Are you trying to tell me that I'm going to get trampled？
I haven't said anything yet.
It'll be fine. When we go to a live house, I will protect you.
Rinko
...Yeah. You know, I think it's okay to grab my hand when that happens...
Sure.
And then... how can I grow taller？
People ofter say that drinking milk is good for you.
...I've been doing that for a long time. I'm not growing at all.
Do you really want to grow that tall？
If you say it like that, it makes Rinko sound a little desperate.
But, you'd be happy if you grew up, wouldn't you？
That's... look, it's for when I walk besides my boyfriend, it'll look... balanced, right？
What？ I think you're fine as you are now, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see...
You don't have to force yourself to match up with me. You're fine as you are, ▲小早川＊▲.
...Thanks. I feel a little better now.
